query.1720: SELECT Player_name FROM player ORDER BY Votes ASC
query.1722: SELECT Player_name ,  residence FROM player WHERE Occupation != "Researcher"
query.1723: SELECT Sponsor_name FROM player WHERE Residence  =  "Brandon" OR Residence  =  "Birtle"
query.1724: SELECT Player_name FROM player ORDER BY Votes DESC LIMIT 1
query.1725: SELECT Occupation ,  COUNT(*) FROM player GROUP BY Occupation
query.1726: SELECT Occupation FROM player GROUP BY Occupation ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1
query.1727: SELECT Residence FROM player GROUP BY Residence HAVING COUNT(*)  >=  2
query.1728: SELECT T3.Player_name ,  T2.coach_name FROM player_coach AS T1 JOIN coach AS T2 ON T1.Coach_ID  =  T2.Coach_ID JOIN player AS T3 ON T1.Player_ID  =  T3.Player_ID
query.1729: SELECT T3.Player_name FROM player_coach AS T1 JOIN coach AS T2 ON T1.Coach_ID  =  T2.Coach_ID JOIN player AS T3 ON T1.Player_ID  =  T3.Player_ID WHERE T2.Rank  =  1
query.1730: SELECT T3.Player_name ,  T3.gender FROM player_coach AS T1 JOIN coach AS T2 ON T1.Coach_ID  =  T2.Coach_ID JOIN player AS T3 ON T1.Player_ID  =  T3.Player_ID WHERE T1.Starting_year  >  2011
query.1731: SELECT T3.Player_name ,  T2.coach_name FROM player_coach AS T1 JOIN coach AS T2 ON T1.Coach_ID  =  T2.Coach_ID JOIN player AS T3 ON T1.Player_ID  =  T3.Player_ID ORDER BY T3.Votes DESC
query.1732: SELECT Player_name FROM player WHERE Player_ID NOT IN (SELECT Player_ID FROM player_coach)
query.1733: SELECT Residence FROM player WHERE gender  =  "M" INTERSECT SELECT Residence FROM player WHERE gender  =  "F"
query.1734: SELECT T1.club_id ,  T1.club_name, count(*) FROM club AS T1 JOIN coach AS T2 ON T1.club_id  =  T2.club_id GROUP BY T1.club_id
query.1735: SELECT T1.club_id ,  T1.gold FROM match_result AS T1 JOIN coach AS T2 ON T1.club_id  =  T2.club_id GROUP BY T1.club_id ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 1
